    "body": "A related suggestion : replace the long text \"To import a notebook, drag ... or **click here**\" by a simple `import notebook` button, along with a tooltip and/or mention in the doc that importing a notebook also works by dragging.\n\n_Edit_:  This would also help save valuable horizontal space for the other buttons. Right now, even on a reasonablly wide window, selecting a single running notebook produces two lines worth of buttons essentially because of the long text.\n"
